-- This is auto-generated code
CREATE DATABASE temp;

USE temp;

ALTER DATABASE temp COLLATE Latin1_General_100_CI_AI_SC_UTF8;

SELECT
YEAR(LEFT(xxdate,10)) as xdate,
COUNT(*)
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://synapsecoursedl10.dfs.core.windows.net/nyc-taxi-data/Monthly_Transportation_Statistics.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        PARSER_VERSION = '1.0',
        HEADER_ROW = FALSE,
        first_row = 2
    ) 
    with
    (
        xxdate VARCHAR(30) 2    )
AS [result]
group by 1
